org.openintents.tools.simulator.model

类 StateModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openintents.tools.simulator.model.StateModel

  • public class StateModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the model for a scenario state. Contains all sensors values in float or float[] format. Supported sensors: temperature, light, proximity, pressure, gravity, linear acceleration, orientation, accelerometer, magnetic field, rotation vector, gyroscope.
    作者:
    ilarele
